
15,01                                Flowers Of Love
15,01                                     ..G.M.

15,01                                  -And there,
15,01                                 on the table,
15,01                                 sat two roses.
15,01                                      One,
15,01                                      red.
15,01                                   The other,
15,01                                     white.
15,01                                      Red,
15,01                                for my passion,
15,01                                 and my blood.
15,01                                     White,
15,01                               for her innocence,
15,01                                 and her soul.
15,01                                 And they sat,
15,01                               winding together,
15,01                                    the red,
15,01                                 and the white.
15,01                                    Winding,
15,01                                     until,
15,01                                     until,
15,01                              they became as one.
15,01                             Red and white sworls,
15,01                                twined together,
15,01                                    in one,
15,01                                    unified,
15,01                                    spirit.
15,01                         Her innocence and my passion,
15,01                             my blood and her soul,
15,01                                   our love,
15,01                            our ultimate sacrifice,
15,01                                     to be,
15,01                                    forever,
15,01                                    as one.
15,01                                     'End'


15,01...Copywrite - Grey Mouser - LiGHT 05/94...
